18 of the 2025-2026 school year a comprehensive character education
19 program for levels K-12. This comprehensive character education
20 program shall be known as the "character curriculum" and shall focus
21 on the students' development of the following character traits:
22 courage, patriotism, citizenship, honesty, fairness, respect for
23 others, kindness, cooperation, self-respect, self-control, courtesy,
24 compassion, tolerance, diligence, generosity, punctuality,
